                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230625-131-off751 t18230625-131-crimeloc755"></join>, and saw the prisoner with another. Mr. Chadwick stopped to look at the fire - the prisoner and one Newman went up to him; the prisoner took hold of his pocket, and immediately drew this handkerchief out, and tucked it up his jacket. I stood close behind and laid hold of him with it.</p>
